node.accessibility_caption: Photo by Sean Hannity on August 17, 2021. May be a cartoon of 2 people, people standing, footwear and text that says 'ONE-ON-ONE WITH FMR. PRESIDENT DONALD TRUMP TUNE INTO Hannity TONIGHT 9PM ET'.

node.text: HANNITY EXCLUSIVE: What’s happening in Afghanistan is a massive failure and the Biden administration needs to answer several tough questions. Rather than taking responsibility and offering solutions, President Joe Biden blamed former President Donald Trump! TONIGHT, former President Trump will comment on the Biden administration’s disastrous withdrawal from Afghanistan. Tune in at 9 PM ET or set your DVR for this “Hannity” EXCLUSIVE interview!

node.text: White House Press Secretary Jen Psaki refused to guarantee that the U.S. would evacuate Americans stuck in Afghanistan after August 31. We cannot leave our fellow Americans behind! TONIGHT on “Hannity,” we’ll bring you expert analysis and reactions to the Biden administration’s disastrous withdrawal from Afghanistan.

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by Sean Hannity on August 17, 2021. May be an image of 1 person and text.

node.text: National Security Advisor Jake Sullivan admitted to reporters that the Taliban has a “fair amount” of abandoned U.S. weapons. That’s what happens when you leave a country after 20 years and don’t have an exit strategy! Now the Taliban has control of the country and is already terrorizing the people of Afghanistan. TONIGHT on “Hannity,” we’ll discuss the Biden administration’s failures in Afghanistan.

node.text: President Biden may have said “the buck stops with me,” but he spent his entire speech on the situation in Afghanistan blaming everyone from Trump to Afghan allies. The Taliban has made major advances since the U.S. began its withdrawal, and now controls the country. TONIGHT on “Hannity,” we’ll bring you expert analysis on the fall of Afghanistan and the Taliban’s takeover. Tune in at 9 PM ET or set your DVR to never miss an episode!

node.accessibility_caption: Photo shared by Sean Hannity on August 16, 2021 tagging @repmichaelwaltz. May be an image of 2 people and text that says 'GOP LAWMAKERS DEMAND ANSWERS ON AFGHANISTAN REP. MICHAEL WALTZ & REP. MIKE MCCAUL TONIGHT ON Hannity'.

node.text: Republicans are demanding answers on Biden’s disastrous withdrawal from Afghanistan. The Biden administration ignored the Trump administration’s plan for a conditions-based withdrawal and now the Taliban has taken Kabul. Rep. Michael Waltz, who served in Afghanistan, and Rep. Mike McCaul will weigh in on the situation TONIGHT on “Hannity.”

node.text: Afghanistan is falling apart, and President Biden is refusing to take responsibility for the Taliban’s takeover. How did this withdrawal go from a planned operation to a Saigon-like disaster? TONIGHT on “Hannity,” Sen. Marco Rubio will discuss Biden’s catastrophic withdrawal from Afghanistan. Tune in at 9 PM ET or set your DVR for this must-see interview!
